@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
title 内部块与接口图

rectangle "Android 手机\nOpenBot App" as Phone <<block>>
rectangle "人物检测与 ReID" as Vision <<block>>
rectangle "目标轨迹/身份信念" as Track <<block>>
rectangle "距离/障碍/安全证据" as Evidence <<block>>
rectangle "状态机与行为仲裁" as FSM <<block>>
rectangle "控制生成" as Control <<block>>
rectangle "ESP32 下位机" as ESP32 <<block>>
rectangle "AT8236 驱动板" as Driver <<block>>
rectangle "四轮底盘" as Chassis <<block>>
rectangle "诊断日志" as Log <<block>>

Phone --> Vision : 相机帧
Vision --> Track : 检测框、ReID 分数、margin
Track --> Evidence : locked/suspected track\nidentity belief
Evidence --> FSM : DistanceState\nTraversability\nSystemSafety
FSM --> Control : BehaviorAction
Control --> ESP32 : c(left,right)\nh(interval)
ESP32 --> Driver : 四轮速度指令\nUART 或 I2C
Driver --> Chassis : 电机 PWM/闭环控制
ESP32 --> Phone : 可选状态回传
FSM --> Log : 状态、动作、reason
Track --> Log : track、belief、gate

note bottom of Control
真实底盘控制尚未接通前，
Control 先进入 Human Cart Simulator 提示。
end note
@enduml
